  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Vulnerable Children in Monze, Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At PIZZ, Mrs. Veronica Sianga and her dedicated team including teachers and care-givers, love and care for more than 500 vulnerable children. All are from very poor families (about half of them orphaned). They give them a lot of support, an excellent education and help them grow in maturity, self esteem and confidence. It is a wonderfully inspiring special place! Sadly, at the moment younger classes are closed during Covid-19 lockdown, meaning a need for even more community support.</narrative>
  </description>
